\f0 \cf2 Box 2 | Adaptive precision-prevention trial design during PIERW
\f1\fs42\fsmilli21333 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs32 \cf3 Proposed biomarker-stratified adaptive platform trial architecture for postoperative Crohn\'92s disease. Patients are stratified according to dominant biological phenotype immediately after surgery and undergo mechanism-directed randomisation with longitudinal Bayesian risk updating. The framework integrates ecological, immunological, imaging and patient-centred outcomes to evaluate precision-prevention pathways rather than isolated therapeutic interventions.
\f2 \
